# Pm

This is the workspace level docs for the Pm framework. There are a few crates.

## pm

The Pm framework directory. This is published.

## mut_cell

A RefCell-like abstraction but with a different goal. It is used by State in Pm. This is published.

## macros

The few proc-macros needed by Pm. This is not published.

## tests

Integrated tests and benchmarks for Pm. This is not published.

## common

Helpful State and Doers used by Pm programs. This is published.

## examples

Examples of how to use Pm. This is not published.
